    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. This example is mechanically robust, featuring a documented VANOS system overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to address chassis fatigue common to the E46 platform. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics, ensuring crisp turn-in and lateral stability. Finished in Silver Grey Metallic, this driver-focused coupe offers linear power delivery and precise throttle modulation, making it an ideal candidate for the spirited purist.",
